# Plan: Add `image-text-to-text` Pipeline to Transformers.js

## Context

The library supports VLM (vision-language model) architectures like LLaVA, Qwen2-VL, SmolVLM, and PaliGemma via `AutoModelForImageTextToText` (in `src/models.js`), but has no high-level pipeline for the `image-text-to-text` task. Users currently must manually wire up the processor, model, and tokenizer. Adding this pipeline provides the same simple `pipeline('image-text-to-text')` interface that exists for other tasks.

**Only `src/pipelines.js` needs modification.** No existing pipeline classes or model code will be changed.

---

## Changes (all in `src/pipelines.js`)

### Step 1: Add import for `AutoModelForImageTextToText`

**Location:** Line ~44, in the import block from `'./models.js'`

Add `AutoModelForImageTextToText` after `AutoModelForImageFeatureExtraction` in the existing import statement.

### Step 2: Add JSDoc type definitions

**Location:** After `ImageToTextPipeline` class (after line 2005), before the `ImageClassificationSingle` typedef (line 2007)

```javascript
/**
 * @typedef {Object} ImageTextToTextSingle
 * @property {string} generated_text The generated text.
 * @typedef {ImageTextToTextSingle[]} ImageTextToTextOutput
 *
 * @callback ImageTextToTextPipelineCallback Generate text based on an image and a text prompt.
 * @param {ImageInput} image The image input.
 * @param {string} text The text prompt.
 * @param {Partial<import('./generation/configuration_utils.js').GenerationConfig>} [options] Additional keyword arguments to pass along to the generate method of the model.
 * @returns {Promise<ImageTextToTextOutput>} An object containing the generated text.
 *
 * @typedef {TextImagePipelineConstructorArgs & ImageTextToTextPipelineCallback & Disposable} ImageTextToTextPipelineType
 */
```

### Step 3: Add `ImageTextToTextPipeline` class

**Location:** Immediately after the JSDoc from Step 2 (still before `ImageClassificationSingle` typedef)

**Key design decision — processor argument order:** VLM processors have inconsistent `_call` signatures:
- **Images-first:** `LlavaProcessor`, `PaliGemmaProcessor`, `Florence2Processor`, `PixtralProcessor`
